Title: Feature transformation by function decomposition  Spec. Issue on Feature Transformation and Subset Selection  
Author: Blaz Zupan Marko Bohanec Janez Demsar Ivan Bratko ; (H. Liu, M. Motoda, eds) 
Keyword: feature transformation, feature construction, feature discovery, function decomposition, hierarchy of features, classification  
Note: To appear in IEEE Expert  
